div.label: English
div.div: Add a one-line explanation of what this file represents

td.div:
English: Tile for the game Tantrix. Filename encodes information:
###A = Tile number and number color
xyz = Van Ness notation of connectivity
jkljkl = colors, counted clockwise starting from left edge, using color scheme (Yellow, Red, Blue, Green assigned to a, b, c with one color missing)
ABCABC = colors, counted clockwise starting from left edge

tr.td: Van Ness, Kurt. Tantrix Tiles. van-ness.com. Retrieved on 9 October 2017.
as described by Kurt Van Ness
